  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Change the Life of a Ugandan Child with Water</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help us deliver clean water to Migyera a rural village of 5,000 people in central Uganda. Today women and children spend an extraordinary amount of time collecting unsanitary water from a local pond. Access to clean water will help students excel in school by improving their health and giving them more time to focus on their studies. It will empower more women to pursue income-generating projects through our programs and dramatically improve the conditions for patients in our health center.</narrative>
  </description>
